schools.name: Wayne Early / Middle College High School

data.description: Gorgeous 4 bedroom, 2 1/2 bathroom home in the quaint neighborhood of Weatherstone!  CBA schools!  Walk into the foyer of this beautiful 2 story home that leads to the formal dining room and open kitchen.  Kitchen has beautiful granite countertops, tile backsplash, stainless appliances and laminate flooring throughout the main level.  Living room also offers gas logs!  1/2 bath on first floor as well.  All bedrooms are upstairs in this home.  Large primary bedroom has huge walk in closet, stand up shower and separate soaker tub.  dual vanity with granite countertops in ALL bathrooms!  3 remaining bedrooms are also large and offer lots of natural light throughout the home.  This home has a HUGE fenced backyard with privacy bushes at the back of the lot. Extra parking slab in driveway as well!
